This is the DBI integration with Monitis.
 - Have a look at monitis_dbi_config_sample.pl - it is self explanatory.
 - Rename it to monitis_dbi_config.pl
 - Edit monitis_config with your API and secret keys
 - To add the configured monitors, use:
# ./monitis_dbi.pl add_monitors
 - To update data:
# ./monitis_dbi.pl update_data
 - For a dry run of data update:
# ./monitis_dbi.pl "update_data(1)"

